latestIgtvVideos.caption: VERY FIRST LOOK AT the Netflix Tudum Bridgerton Season 3 carriage and the Bridgerton set and Queen Charlotte orangery experience in Brazil! You saw it at the same time as me! Key Easter egg details: green carriage, butterflies! Love you all so much! #tudum #netflix #bridgerton #bridgertonseason3 #polin

latestIgtvVideos.title: 10.05.19 💕
latestIgtvVideos.caption: We have spent almost every waking moment together for the majority of the last wildly unpredictable 12 months, and the thing I’m most excited for at the end of each day is to cuddle up and spend even MORE time with you. Thank you for being my favorite person in the world. Life is so much better with you in it @bobbyjsimpson. Re-living our  day thanks to @northmarkfilms ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Formal Zoom Dinner Facials with Renee Rouleau
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Celebrity facialist @reneerouleau walks me through a 5-step at-home facial while answering your questions on acne, dark marks, KP, and Botox alternatives! Thanks for joining #formalzoomdinner!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Joey Healy Gives Me A Virtual Brow Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Brow master @joeyhealybrows gave me a virtual brow tutorial! Follow along from start to finish with his universal tips — and stick around as he answers your top questions! If you groom your brows with us, tag us so we can see the final result!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Formal Zoom Dinner: Denise Bidot
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Model @denisebidot teaches me how to contour (she went to makeup school, ya’ll!), pose (say “you’re a bad bitch” to yourself in your head), look 35 when you’re 65 (Vaseline!), and find confidence in the things that make you YOU. thank you for another incredible chat, and for bringing so much light and positivity to the industry! 💕 #formalzoomdinner

latestIgtvVideos.title: Nam Vo Shares Her Highlighting Tricks & Product Picks
Cat’s Sock Curl Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption: After the age-old #sockcurls technique made a comeback on TikTok, and I saw @justinemarjan’s flawless execution, I had to try it myself. Watch to the end to see how it turned out. I think my Grandma Lollie would be proud. 🥰 What hair tutorials do you want to see next? ✨✨

latestIgtvVideos.title: My Loungewear Makeup Routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Like high-end yoga pants — but for your face. These are the 5 most comfortable, easy-to-apply products I’m wearing at home right now. What are your favorite loungewear makeup products?

latestIgtvVideos.title: Rihanna Shares Fenty’s Inclusive Shade Range — & The Inspiration Behind It
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Everyone needs to hear Rihanna talk about why creating inclusive makeup shades is so important. 👏👏🏻👏🏽👏🏾👏🏿 new full video from her launch party last year, thanks to IGTV!

Ginny and Georgia season 3 stars Brianne Howey and Antonia Gentry reveal that half the cast starred in Degrassi - plus other hidden details on set, what they’d do if they were on house arrest like Georgia, and more. Ginny & Georgia is streaming now on @netflix. @imdb #IMDbpartner

Georgia Miller is the only one wearing a red lip in Ginny and Georgia — until season 3 when her character breaks down and is placed under house arrest. Brianne Howey shares the reason for Georgia’s season 3 makeunder, and Antonia Gentry, who plays her daughter Ginny on the show, talks about the confidence she got from her characters new longer hair extensions. #IMDbpartner @imdb

Why did Marcus cut his hair in Ginny and Georgia season 3? Actor Felix Mallard weighs in on the meaning behind his character’s haircut, which his on-screen twin Max (Sarah Waisglass) says “is a cry for help.” What do you think of the cut? #IMDbpartner @imdb
